projects.name: Game Of Life
projects.description: This is a game called Game of life challenge. The Game of Life, also known simply as Life, is a cellular automaton devised by the British mathematician John Horton Conway in 1970.

projects.name: Galsen Mangas
projects.description: An app offering free access to anime, manga, and novels, packed with features for a seamless and enjoyable experience.

projects.name: Galsen Coding Challenge
projects.description: This project aims to create a platform for coding challenges and collaboration within the Senegalese coding community. Users can participate in challenges, create their own, and engage in collaborative coding efforts.

projects.name: Sama Keur
projects.description: SamaKeur is a user-friendly real estate platform where users can register using their email address or Google account. They have the ability to add, delete, and modify real estate rental or sale listings with ease. Find your dream home or a reliable tenant in the blink of an eye thanks to SamaKeur.

projects.name: Game Of Life

projects.name: Tech Survey
projects.description: The goal of this project is to establish a platform dedicated to conducting salary surveys for developers in Senegal. Users have the ability to participate in surveys, create their own surveys, and access all survey data within the platform.

projects.name: Blog App
projects.description: A very simple mobile application that allows users to add blogs, view blog details, developed with Java and SQLite for the database.

projects.name: Jayy Ma Baguette
projects.description: JayyMaBaguette is a landing page for a baker. It has 7 sections: the header, the category section, the about us section, the menu section, the product presentation section, the contact form, and the footer.

projects.name: Sama Car
projects.description: Sama Car is a landing page for a car business. It is a React application, styled using Tailwind CSS. The landing page aims to showcase the car business and its offerings to potential customers in an engaging and visually appealing manner.

projects.name: Sen Coffee
projects.description: Sen Coffee is a homepage for a coffee shop. It is a React application styled with Tailwind CSS. The purpose of this homepage is to present the coffee business and its products in an attractive and visually appealing way to potential customers.

projects.name: Sama Contacts
projects.description: The Contacts Management System is a web application that allows users to manage their contacts. It provides functionalities such as adding new contacts, editing existing ones, and categorizing contacts into different categories.
